      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under formal configuration management with documented version control and regression testing at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is used under institutional software quality assurance procedures. Version control, release notes, and regression test suite documentation confirm Gradation 2 compliance. No anomalies identified during the assessment period."
