      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct numerical implementation via method of manufactured solutions or equivalent benchmark with documented convergence rates.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations confirms second-order spatial convergence in L2 norm for velocity components and pressure. Results consistent with published solver benchmarks for rotating machinery applications."
