      "acceptanceCriteria": "Discretization error for hemolysis index QoI must be quantified and bounded below 10% via systematic mesh refinement study.",
      "rationale": "Three-level structured mesh refinement study performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry. Richardson extrapolation yields discretization error of 4.1% for the hemolysis index across all five operating conditions. Grid convergence index confirms asymptotic convergence. Final production mesh of 4.2M cells selected."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
