      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation must be documented with sufficient detail to reproduce boundary conditions in the CFD model.",
      "rationale": "Published experimental dataset (Morrison et al., 2019) provides complete documentation of inlet flow rates, rotational speeds, fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C, 40% hematocrit), and measurement uncertainty. All five flow-speed operating points fully characterized for boundary condition specification."
