      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be conducted on geometry and operating conditions sufficiently representative of the COU to support credibility claims at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry, which is the same device class and operating regime as the COU. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB flow range (2–6 L/min) and rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM). Geometric similarity and flow regime correspondence confirmed at Gradation 2."
    },
    {
