      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second qualified CFD analyst. Analyst credentials and training records on file. Independent re-execution of the full simulation campaign is not required at MRL 2 and has not been conducted."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
