      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, documented justification of turbulence model and hemolysis damage model selection is sufficient; formal model form error quantification not required.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating blood pump applications. Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied with documented parameter values. Formal model form error quantification is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed."
    },
    {
