      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, documented sources for all model input parameters with nominal values are sufficient; probabilistic input characterization not required.",
      "rationale": "All model input parameters documented with sources: fluid viscosity from published blood rheology data, pump geometry from FDA benchmark specifications, boundary conditions from experimental dataset. Probabilistic characterization of input uncertainty is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed."
