    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 with documented justification. CFD predictions of hemolysis index satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five CPB operating conditions with mean absolute error of 6.3%. The computational model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device as specified in the COU. Assessment package accepted for regulatory submission.",
